{"tid":2442684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子看不爽有黑人在海釣，嗆「尼哥滾回去岸上」，最後被網友出征狼狽求饒","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T13:46:09.000Z","uid":202966,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e28770692043c7aad7dea19c6b3d0264b7f1ccda","tid":2442684,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iFCeallmt4Q/YEoQRlJCF3I/AAAAAAAATLU/-zGe9fsUSfcwBlYj_7Dcn_3D7DgHxI0FACLcBGAsYHQ/s600/219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-iFCeallmt4Q%2FYEoQRlJCF3I%2FAAAAAAAATLU%2F-zGe9fsUSfcwBlYj_7Dcn_3D7DgHxI0FACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs600%2F219.jpg&h=8b546dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有個黑人和朋友出海釣魚，結果遇到幾名男子三番兩次威脅挑釁，過程中還嗆歧視字眼「尼哥」，離譜行徑引發網友出征，歧視男看風波越燒越大，最後只能狼狽求饒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kP-iXUALIjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkP-iXUALIjc&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=b3990b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kP-iXUALIjc</a><br />\n這起事件日前發生在美國佛羅里達州的斯圖爾特 (Stuart)，據拍攝影片的Shannon Bustamante表示，當天他受到一個船長朋友邀請，一夥人坐船出海釣魚，其中也包含一名黑人朋友。<br />\n<br />\n一行人抵達漁場後準備開始釣魚，此時卻有一艘叫做「亞曼達V」(Amanda V) 的船開始朝他們咆哮，不想惹事的船長當下決定離開，結果30分鐘後這艘船竟然又主動追上他們找麻煩，Bustamante說對方就是看不慣他們的黑人朋友，所以當天他們也只是「找理由」要來惹事，事實上當天Bustamante一行人根本就沒有主動接近他們。<br />\n<br />\n衝突過後Bustamante把當天的影片分享到網路，很快就有國外的鍵盤柯南找到了這艘船的船籍資料和主人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5V7Q0qqw8gY/YEoQ-GMdNsI/AAAAAAAATLc/DDZIdwWF_aA5YKTHkqqzUsw1xSy6jTfzwCLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h30/ama.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-5V7Q0qqw8gY%2FYEoQ-GMdNsI%2FAAAAAAAATLc%2FDDZIdwWF_aA5YKTHkqqzUsw1xSy6jTfzwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw640-h30%2Fama.jpg&h=52d2c80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據資料顯示這艘船的主人叫做Anthony Puleo，網友查出他是當地一家園藝景觀公司的老闆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-aGXsM3WjfQk/YEoRMu06I6I/AAAAAAAATLg/4S0qk8b9JVoMYXtuveSmST8mPxzv3Y3fACLcBGAsYHQ/w300-h400/ap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-aGXsM3WjfQk%2FYEoRMu06I6I%2FAAAAAAAATLg%2F4S0qk8b9JVoMYXtuveSmST8mPxzv3Y3fACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw300-h400%2Fap.jpg&h=9e0da364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而他的公司官網也馬上被憤怒網友出征，伺服器更因為瞬間湧入的流量直接掛掉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KssejiqHado/YEoRUm5eA4I/AAAAAAAATLo/pAzTEP-gL7wGToZJweUY4l0kyqZUEDzwwCLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h80/band.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-KssejiqHado%2FYEoRUm5eA4I%2FAAAAAAAATLo%2FpAzTEP-gL7wGToZJweUY4l0kyqZUEDzwwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw640-h80%2Fband.jpg&h=618af2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外他公司的商家頁面也被許多網友洗了一星負評，有人說「希望這個極品垃圾人得到報應」，有人嘲諷「老闆有種族歧視，這種人沒資格進我家裡」，還有以前的老客人特地回來留評價說：「這種歧視的垃圾公司以後別想要再做我的生意」：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FOCvH2g3AxY/YEoX0iwj6DI/AAAAAAAATMM/WGB4r_h8p2kbg-3X6jfbTb3uROGRM2fUACLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h468/1st.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-FOCvH2g3AxY%2FYEoX0iwj6DI%2FAAAAAAAATMM%2FWGB4r_h8p2kbg-3X6jfbTb3uROGRM2fUACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw640-h468%2F1st.jpg&h=2a455ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而根據國外媒體報導，事件爆發後，有一位當時在亞曼達V船上的男子主動聯繫記者，但對方聲稱他當天並沒有講歧視的字眼，並拒絕受訪。<br />\n<br />\n但神通廣大的網友馬上查出Anthony Puleo在2014年時曾因為違反保釋規定被逮捕，而船上另外一名男子的身分也被搜出，叫做Nicholas Tozer，身分曝光後兩人都很快將自己的臉書給關閉。<br />\n<br />\n後來影片拍攝者Shannon Bustamante在他自己的Youtube留言區分享了後續，他說目前這三人都意識到了事情的嚴重性，挫咧等的他們不斷乞求原諒：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-uT_aO31RjtU/YEoSMQR5OzI/AAAAAAAATL8/TpvbfUOqx3wfTc223B7dxtfgyEIPaXmiQCLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h106/001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uT_aO31RjtU%2FYEoSMQR5OzI%2FAAAAAAAATL8%2FTpvbfUOqx3wfTc223B7dxtfgyEIPaXmiQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw640-h106%2F001.jpg&h=8659b9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來Bustamante又進一步透露說，亞曼達V上的一名男子有主動跟他聯絡，並威脅說要告他，結果Bustamante回嗆說你就算告我也解決不了問題，後來男子又開始軟化，希望Bustamante能幫他跟大家說他很抱歉，然後還一直哀求說「這件事會毀了我的人生」：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D3lVdo6LTzo/YEoShF8Vf0I/AAAAAAAATME/H3Cog5lkh8wgBaIv5yTGkFGFqL-cIy_NQCLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h82/002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-D3lVdo6LTzo%2FYEoShF8Vf0I%2FAAAAAAAATME%2FH3Cog5lkh8wgBaIv5yTGkFGFqL-cIy_NQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw640-h82%2F002.jpg&h=c342d478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過Bustamante並不打算原諒這些人，之後他準備將完整影片連同亞曼達V的船籍資訊，一同寄給佛羅里達州魚類及野生動物保護委員會 (Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission)，沒意外的話亞曼達V將會被吊銷其擁有的商業捕魚執照。"},{"pid":"b61f3d32a6ae1345e113cfa0b3281127087c66a4","tid":2442684,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">大J原來有玩原神 唔知佢有冇課金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主條撚樣無證無據屈鳩完人，道歉都無句想不停出post洗底</p>"},{"pid":"f09bfe178a4f16a451ffd8fb04af3a560a281542","tid":2442684,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4cypzq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4cypzq.gif&h=b97d5ba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1470489f4fe788878ca744962e0c7acf18c2a29","tid":2442684,"uid":130402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"大J原來有玩原神 唔知佢有冇課金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主條撚樣無證無據屈鳩完人，道歉都無句想不停出post洗底"},{"pid":"ea0ac9cabd4e13e140c0856bfe6d214d55d3315f","tid":2442684,"uid":251477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"大J原來有玩原神 唔知佢有冇課金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主條撚樣無證無據屈鳩完人，道歉都無句想不停出post洗底"},{"pid":"48265ed9d760385b50264363f914a5211a741e31","tid":2442684,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"咁個黑人又真係無做野做乜屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834d5180a28b2e69f0df7897a96244555a92d786","tid":2442684,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"今次我地撐個尼哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb922b72b0a9e77636c6556f2ff96d9fa02ba18","tid":2442684,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48265ed9d760385b50264363f914a5211a741e31","tid":2442684,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"咁個黑人又真係無做野做乜屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"種族歧視係唔會消失"},{"pid":"e911fbb94184fac750f8db9c4e7cef0fa1a4540a","tid":2442684,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb922b72b0a9e77636c6556f2ff96d9fa02ba18","tid":2442684,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48265ed9d760385b50264363f914a5211a741e31","tid":2442684,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"咁個黑人又真係無做野做乜屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"種族歧視係唔會消失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"我有諗過種歧視唔會消失係班白左而唔係極右"}]}